57#include <openssl/asn1.h>
58
59#include <openssl/asn1t.h>
60
61
62/* Declarations for string types */
63
64#define IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(sname) \
65 IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE(sname) \
66 IMPLEMENT_ASN1_ENCODE_FUNCTIONS_fname(sname, sname, sname) \
67 sname *sname##_new(void) \
68 { \
69 return ASN1_STRING_type_new(V_##sname); \
70 } \
71 void sname##_free(sname *x) \
72 { \
73 ASN1_STRING_free(x); \
74 }
75
76IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_OCTET_STRING)
77IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_INTEGER)
78IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_ENUMERATED)
79IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_BIT_STRING)
80IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_UTF8STRING)
81IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_PRINTABLESTRING)
82IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_T61STRING)
83IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_IA5STRING)
84IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_GENERALSTRING)
85IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_UTCTIME)
86IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_GENERALIZEDTIME)
87IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_VISIBLESTRING)
88IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_UNIVERSALSTRING)
89IMPLEMENT_ASN1_STRING_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_BMPSTRING)
90
91IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE(ASN1_NULL);
92IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(ASN1_NULL);
93
94IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE(ASN1_OBJECT);
95
96IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE(ASN1_ANY);
97
98/* Just swallow an ASN1_SEQUENCE in an ASN1_STRING */;
99IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE(ASN1_SEQUENCE);
100
101IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS_fname(ASN1_TYPE, ASN1_ANY, ASN1_TYPE);
102
103/* Multistring types */;
104
105IMPLEMENT_ASN1_MSTRING(ASN1_PRINTABLE, B_ASN1_PRINTABLE);
106IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS_name(ASN1_STRING, ASN1_PRINTABLE);
107
108IMPLEMENT_ASN1_MSTRING(DISPLAYTEXT, B_ASN1_DISPLAYTEXT);
109IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS_name(ASN1_STRING, DISPLAYTEXT);
110
111IMPLEMENT_ASN1_MSTRING(DIRECTORYSTRING, B_ASN1_DIRECTORYSTRING);
112IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS_name(ASN1_STRING, DIRECTORYSTRING);
113
114/* Three separate BOOLEAN type: normal, DEFAULT TRUE and DEFAULT FALSE */;
115IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE_ex(ASN1_BOOLEAN, ASN1_BOOLEAN, -1);
116IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE_ex(ASN1_TBOOLEAN, ASN1_BOOLEAN, 1);
117IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE_ex(ASN1_FBOOLEAN, ASN1_BOOLEAN, 0);
118
119/* Special, OCTET STRING with indefinite length constructed support */;
120
121IMPLEMENT_ASN1_TYPE_ex(ASN1_OCTET_STRING_NDEF, ASN1_OCTET_STRING,
122 ASN1_TFLG_NDEF);
123
124ASN1_ITEM_TEMPLATE(ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY) = ASN1_EX_TEMPLATE_TYPE(
125 ASN1_TFLG_SEQUENCE_OF, 0, ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY, ASN1_ANY);
126ASN1_ITEM_TEMPLATE_END(ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY);
127
128ASN1_ITEM_TEMPLATE(ASN1_SET_ANY) = ASN1_EX_TEMPLATE_TYPE(ASN1_TFLG_SET_OF, 0,
129 ASN1_SET_ANY,
130 ASN1_ANY);
131ASN1_ITEM_TEMPLATE_END(ASN1_SET_ANY);
132
133IMPLEMENT_ASN1_ENCODE_FUNCTIONS_const_fname(ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY,
134 ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY,
135 ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY);
136IMPLEMENT_ASN1_ENCODE_FUNCTIONS_const_fname(ASN1_SEQUENCE_ANY, ASN1_SET_ANY,
137 ASN1_SET_ANY);
